gw.api.json.mapping

Interface JsonMapping


  • public interface JsonMapping
    Class that represents a collection of mappings that target a particular schema graph at a particular version.

      • getFullyQualifiedName

        @NotNull
@NotNull java.lang.String getFullyQualifiedName()
        Returns the fully-qualified name of this mapping, i.e. <name>-<version>. This is the name that should be used to reference the mapping from other places, such as imports, combines, or when retrieving the mapping by name via the JsonConfigAccess class.
        Returns:
        the fully-qualified name of this mapping
